On this form, you can also select your time zone, which will be used by the system to define the business date for your sessions. (The default time zone for the business date is specified by the portal system administrator.) ==Related Articles== *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__how_Change_Password|To Change Your Password] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP_40_80_45|User Profile] ([~/?ScreenId=SP408045|SP408045])

