d. |- | '''Severity''' | The severity level of the case, which is one of the following options: ''High'', ''Low'', ''Medium''. |- | '''Priority''' | The priority of the case. The following options are available: ''High'', ''Low'', and ''Medium''. |} ==Activities Tab== This tab has a table with the list of activities associated with the case. When you add a comment, the system displays it in the table. Click any activity to view the contents of the comment in the text (lower) area of the tab.{br}
