In the modern user interface of Self-Service Portal, existing elements were redesigned and new elements are introduced, which provide you with enhanced visualization and flexibility in configuring the navigation items. The modern user interface makes your work in the system convenient and easy because you can configure it to better fit your working tasks.{br}
This chapter describes the new and redesigned elements of the user interface. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_caaff54f-75ed-489d-b993-79e05e657136] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_20c6da3c-5566-4025-8d3b-6c34bad4728b] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Basic_Elements|Basic Elements of the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Info_Area|Info Area in the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Search|Search in the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Main_Menu|Main Menu in the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Workspaces|Workspaces in the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Menu_Editing_Mode|Menu Editing Mode in the Modern UI] *[HelpRoot_Portal\SP__con_New_UI_Help|Help in the Modern UI]
