Each table on an Self-Service Portal form or dialog box has a table toolbar, which contains buttons you can use to work with the details or objects of the table.{br}
The table toolbar buttons are grouped into sections:[anchor|#ul_q5x_rn2_n3] *''Action section'': Contains buttons that are specific to the form and standard buttons that most table toolbars have. *''Filter section'': Contains a box you can use to select a filter (to filter data in the table) and related buttons.
The ''footer'' displays navigation buttons if there are too many details or objects (that is, table rows) to fit on one page.[anchor|#image_dfk_1k2_33][image:Portal/Images/details_toolbar.png|popup|Table toolbar|300px][anchor|#ol_ohv_zj2_33] #Action section #Filter section #Footer
